SUMMARY:Movie Night | Ep. 51 - Lisa Frankenstein (2024)
DESCRIPTION:Dinosaurs return, the park is definitely open, and nothing
 could possibly go wrong. Perfect Sunday night viewing with chat. Meet you
 all on Discord for Movie Night.
URL:https://www.twitch.tv/dr_ravenholm
CATEGORIES:Movie Night
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
