UID:stream-22422211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260126T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260220T003400Z
DTSTART:20260216T213000Z
DTEND:20260216T233000Z
SUMMARY:Motor Town: Behind The Wheel | Ep. 17 - This Delivery Felt Closer
 on the Map
DESCRIPTION:A simple job. A short route. Absolutely no unexpected
 detours... probably. Enjoy realistic driving in the open world. Relaxing
 cargo deliveries or driving buses and taxis will give you enough money to
 buy new cars and parts. You can test your driving skills at the race
 track. It's all about pure driving pleasure!
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qTvA-votD6c
CATEGORIES:Motor Town: Behind The Wheel
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-22432211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260127T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260220T003400Z
DTSTART:20260217T213000Z
DTEND:20260217T233000Z
SUMMARY:Star Trek Online | Ep. 9 - At Least it's not Starfleet Academy
DESCRIPTION:More deep-space adventure, fewer awkward cadet training
 exercises. Hopefully. In Star Trek Online, the Star Trek universe appears
 for the first time on a truly massive scale. Players take the captain's
 chair as they command their own starship and crew. Explore strange new
 worlds, seek out new life and new civilizations, and boldly go where no
 one has gone before.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1UjavCEOC1g
CATEGORIES:Star Trek Online
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-22442211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260128T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260220T003400Z
DTSTART:20260218T213000Z
DTEND:20260218T233000Z
SUMMARY:Sniper Elite V2 Remastered | Ep. 1 - Prologue & Schöneberg Convoy
DESCRIPTION:Stealth, precision, and cinematic slow-motion shots. We're
 stepping into WWII tactical action - and aiming carefully. In the dark
 days of the end of World War 2 amidst the ruins of Berlin, one bullet can
 change history... Elite sniper Karl Fairburne returns to the front line in
 the remaster of this award-winning stealth-action experience. Packed with
 new features, contemporary visuals and definitive content.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QPijthXhemQ
CATEGORIES:Sniper Elite V2 Remastered
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-22452211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260129T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260220T003400Z
DTSTART:20260219T213000Z
DTEND:20260219T233000Z
SUMMARY:Star Trek: Voyager - Across the Unknown | Ep. 1 - There's Coffee
 in That Nebula
DESCRIPTION:A brand-new journey begins in the Delta Quadrant. Exploration,
 mystery, and coffee-fueled determination. Star Trek: Voyager - Across the
 Unknown is a story-driven survival strategy game in which the fate of the
 iconic starship is in your hands. Take the helm, manage the ship and
 resources, and make difficult decisions. Will you be able to bring home
 the ship and its crew?
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gA5Gv2ON1lM
CATEGORIES:Star Trek: Voyager - Across the Unknown
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
